==Reception==
The fight was sold-out, grossing {{US$|15 million}} at the live gate, the fourth highest of any boxing event in Las Vegas.<ref name="boxingscene">{{cite news|title=Mayweather-Maidana: Highest Selling PPV Of 2014, But…|url=https://www.boxingscene.com/mayweather-maidana-highest-selling-ppv-2014--77979|work=BoxingScene|date=19 May 2014|language=en-us}}</ref> The event sold an estimated 900,000 buys on [[pay-per-view]],<ref>{{cite news|title=Mayweather-Maidana fight generates less than 1 million pay per view buys|url=https://www.si.com/boxing/counter-punch/2014/05/29/floyd-mayweather-marcos-maidana-boxing|work=[[Sports Illustrated]]|date=May 29, 2014|language=en}}</ref> the year's highest-selling PPV up until May 2014, grossing an estimated $63{{nbsp}}million in pay-per-view revenue, bringing the event's total revenue up to an estimated ${{#expr:63+15}}{{nbsp}}million.<ref name="boxingscene"/>

==Fight purses==
Guaranteed fight purses: Over $37{{nbsp}}million total (including most expensive undercard in pay-per-view history, as of May 2014)<ref name="boxingscene"/>

