*Floyd Mayweather ($32,000,000) vs. Marcos Maidana ($1,500,000)<ref name="mlive">{{cite news|title=Floyd Mayweather's base purse $32 million for fighting Marcos Maidana|url=http://www.mlive.com/mayweather/2014/04/floyd_mayweathers_base_purse_3.html|work=[[MLive]]|date=30 April 2014}}</ref>

;Undercard
